data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Under contract, receiving backup offers! One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome to your lovely new home in Chelsea Landing, Hunters Creek!  WOW! describes this home and its location!    Residents are within very short distances to award winning A-rated elementary and middle schools, as well as Osprey Park which is one of the seven community parks in the Hunter's Creek area. It is the largest of the parks, and has several sports fields, as well as nature trails and areas for picnicking.    Enjoy living close to The Loop, A casual, pedestrian friendly, open air shopping center with wonderful retail, dining and entertainment, making everyday conveniences just minutes away.  Having close proximity to 417, 528, the Florida Turnpike, and I-4 is also great to get anywhere in Central Florida!    This home features a new roof, new AC with upgraded tile and hardwood flooring throughout for easy maintenance.  The house comes equipped with TESLA SOLAR PANELS INCLUDED IN THE PRICE!  Relax in your screened lanai for morning coffee or evening sunsets and enjoy the privacy of a fenced yard.  Enjoy plenty of storage and modern cabinetry in the kitchen with high ceilings for plenty of light and space.  This move in ready home is waiting for your style to make it your own.  4 bedrooms gives you flexibility for an office, gym, guest room or growing family.    Hunters Creek is in close proximity to the Lake Buena Vista area and the Disney theme parks, so you'll definitely want to take advantage of Florida Resident discounts on annual passes and  makes it easy to visit even just for a few hours after work on a weeknight.
